{
  "stem": "15540.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he did know a lot of people in the, in the higher echelons in the industry and in the, in the foreign ministry.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that is where he, he dealt with a lot of people there, because of his company exporting.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he would-- those last months was in constant contact with them to find out if there was anything about the rumors that by then had started going, that, that there would be action against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, my mother was not brought up with anything, as far as Jewish religion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was extremely assimilated and, and just couldn't believe that this would happen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even after we had fled from Copenhagen, she refused to leave Denmark until she heard that actually the action had taken place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it started about the, the 26th of September.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the first night that my father came home and said that we would have to pack up some things and, and, and leave the house and not stay in the house at night because of the rumors that were going on.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was a time that they explained to us that we were Jewish and, and tried to explain to us what that meant and why, why we had to leave our house.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that night we slept at, at a neighbor's house, in the basement.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But nothing happened that night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the next day we went back and went back to school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the 27th, that night we slept at home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was just before I-- my ninth birthday.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
